# AquaBot 💧

An AI-powered chatbot that answers queries about groundwater levels, quality, and conservation tips.

## 🚀 Features
- Natural language Q&A on groundwater topics
- Conservation tips and educational responses
- Clean chat interface
- Fast, AI-generated answers

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
React, Node.js, Express, AI API (Claude/Gemini/OpenAI)

