## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

1. Clone the repository
```bash
git clone <your-repo-link>
cd aquabot
```

2. Install dependencies (frontend & backend)
```bash
cd client && npm install
cd ../server && npm install
```

3. Run the app
```bash
# Backend
npm run dev

# Frontend (new terminal)
cd client && npm run dev
```

